{"name": "mattermost-py-api", "metadata": {"name": "mattermost-py-api", "version": "1.0.3", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "https://github.com/jlandells/mm-py-api", "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["requests"], "summary": "A simple Python library for making Mattermost API calls", "upload_time": 1732293774}, "documentation": ["![Unit Tests](https://github.com/jlandells/mm-py-api/actions/workflows/unit-tests.yml/badge.svg)\n\n\n# Mattermost API Library\n\nA simple Python library for making Mattermost API calls.\n\n## Installation\n\nInstall directly from GitHub:\n\n```bash\npip install git+https://github.com/jlandells/mm-py-api.git\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n```python\nfrom mattermost_api import make_mattermost_api_call\n\nresponse = make_mattermost_api_call(\n    mattermost_url=\"https://example.com\",\n    api_token=\"your_token\",\n    endpoint=\"/api/v4/users/me\",\n)\nprint(response)\n```\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "mattermost_api", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "mattermost_api.mattermost_api", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "mattermost_api.mattermost_api.make_mattermost_api_call", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "mattermost_url", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "api_token", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "endpoint", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "method", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "port", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "json_body", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Dict", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "params", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Dict", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}]}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "Dict", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": ["Makes an API call to a Mattermost server and returns the response as a dictionary.\n\nArgs:\n    mattermost_url (str): The base URL of the Mattermost server (e.g., 'https://example.com').\n    api_token (str): The personal access token for authentication.\n    endpoint (str): The API endpoint (e.g., '/api/v4/users/me').\n    method (str): The HTTP method to use ('GET', 'POST', 'PATCH', 'DELETE', etc.).\n    port (int): The port on which Mattermost is running. Default is 8065.\n    json_body (Optional[Dict[str, Any]]): The JSON body for the request (default is None).\n    params (Optional[Dict[str, str]]): Query parameters for the request (default is None).\n\nReturns:\n    Dict[str, Any]: The JSON response as a dictionary.\n\nRaises:\n    requests.exceptions.RequestException: If the HTTP request fails."]}], "vari